title: snowflake.snowpark.Session.stored_procedure_profiler | Snowflake Documentation
paragraphs:
Returns a stored_procedure_profiler.StoredProcedureProfiler object that you can use to profile stored procedures.
See details of how to use this object in stored_procedure_profiler.StoredProcedureProfiler.
This function or method is in private preview since 1.23.0.
